{
  "comment_text": {
    "sn1.30:1.1": "A similar exchange is found at <a href='https://suttacentral.net/snp1.9/en/sujato#15.1'>Snp 1.9:15.1</a>, there spoken by two <i lang='pi' translate='no'>yakkhas</i>. | “Antelope calves” are one opf the thirty-two marks of a great man, for which see <a href='https://suttacentral.net/dn14/en/sujato#1.32.25'>DN 14:1.32.25</a>, <a href='https://suttacentral.net/dn30/en/sujato#1.22.6'>DN 30:1.22.6</a>. "
  },
